                <h1>How a Misdemeanor DUI Can Impact Your Job Prospects</h1>
                <p>A misdemeanor DUI can impact employment opportunities, particularly in fields requiring driving or a clean background check. Employers may scrutinize candidates with such records, assessing their trustworthiness and reliability. However, the effects can vary widely by industry, employer policies, and time since the offense.</p>
